Fonts

Bundled font files in assets/fonts/ and temp_fonts/ are third-party font
software and are not relicensed under MIT. They include Source Han Sans JP,
Space Mono, Hachi Maru Pop, Reggae One, Yuji Syuku, and Zen Kurenaido. Source
Han Sans JP is licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1; see
temp_fonts/LICENSE.txt. Other bundled fonts should be used under their
respective upstream font licenses.

